'''''United''''' is a 1984 video game published by [[Cases Computer Simulations Ltd]].

==Gameplay==
''United'' is a game in which the player manages and builds a [[Football League Fourth Division|fourth division]] [[Association football|football]] team, get them to win the league Championship.<ref name="Imagine22"/>

==Reception==
Luke Renouf reviewed ''United'' for ''[[Imagine (AD&D magazine)|Imagine]]'' magazine, and stated that "it's a good and fairly difficult game which has an addictive quality that will keep you coming back for more."<ref name="Imagine22">{{cite journal | last = Renouf |first = Luke | title =Micro Reviews | type = review | journal = [[Imagine (game magazine)|Imagine]] | issue = 22| pages =39 | publisher = TSR Hobbies (UK), Ltd. |date=January 1985}}</ref>

